{"tid":1677010,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[安全問題]使用蘇聯豬嘴的手足請 立 即 停 止 使用 原裝 filter","createTime":"2019-10-26T20:02:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T14:03:12.000Z","uid":40672,"like":327,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"6725fbbafda0f07dd63fcb6991f085f0ef7e7f42","tid":1677010,"uid":40672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T20:02:10.000Z","msg":"如果你用緊Gp5/7 pmk 系列filter的話，請立即停止使用原裝Filter<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HVgyU9J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHVgyU9J.jpg&h=3266b9e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n講緊你呀手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原裝綠色嗰隻Filter含有石棉，基本上所有蘇聯年代 不論軍民用嘅Gas mask Filter都會含有大約3%石棉<br />\n<br />\n如非必要切勿使用，畢竟蘇聯都收皮咁多年隨時老過你，入面既Filter組成可能會有解體/鬆動嘅可能<br />\n吸入石棉會導致好多肺部related嘅疾病，死得好撚慘<br />\n<br />\n解決方法：買過啲Filter喇，例如FP-5就平靚正<br />\n買嘅時侯小心，醫悲上面好多都係北約款嘅filter，北約同華約嘅Filter螺絲係有少少分別，唔可以混用（唔氣密）。<br />\n華約嗰隻叫GOST，北約係STANAG 有啲Filter係設計到兩隻標準都可以裝到兼氣密，選購嘅時候小心留意<br />\n<br />\n如果有心買的話，不妨考慮下買以色列豬嘴（Shalon 4A1） Amazon50美金有找<br />\n再唔係的話買支那fmj08 全身600 700人民幣有找，呢兩隻豬嘴北約定係華約Filter都可以用，又平靚正"},{"pid":"a855809508bf8b89e783f04b15e44c238e15f09c","tid":1677010,"uid":137265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T20:05:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"edbe6c13346112aeb2b89853c0963a24e767653e","tid":1677010,"uid":172465,"like":92,"dislike":0,"score":92,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T20:07:09.000Z","msg":"俄佬野除左AK RPG同俄妹之外都唔多信得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手足快啲換新裝"},{"pid":"34c841373b981953a68c86e3e855531233a372d1","tid":1677010,"uid":40672,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"edbe6c13346112aeb2b89853c0963a24e767653e","tid":1677010,"uid":172465,"like":92,"dislike":0,"score":92,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T20:07:09.000Z","msg":"俄佬野除左AK RPG同俄妹之外都唔多信得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手足快啲換新裝"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T20:15:41.000Z","msg":"係個filter姐<br />\n如果係全身啱啱出廠我會夠膽用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19fe8083199eb857881d48a7099a17dcbbed676d","tid":1677010,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T20:17:07.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n祝大家裝修健康"},{"pid":"0cad9d30dfb72dad6ce9d17e9f4cda7faf14b568","tid":1677010,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T20:32:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rG9c5Um.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrG9c5Um.gif&h=4ad4d108&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"103549a738bc0339c757711eb65031a06e5eb4b5","tid":1677010,"uid":15379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T20:50:50.000Z","msg":"有用推"},{"pid":"6b7586eb3525f8154247563a1dbf9854af4fcb34","tid":1677010,"uid":3295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T22:51:54.000Z","msg":"推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dc5e652f6421175b387d9e06d409ea29629406f","tid":1677010,"uid":48766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T23:15:15.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"d5a988dcc955b10d32cb62dc4de0e688a1dc2be9","tid":1677010,"uid":40672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:32:55.000Z","msg":"琴日仲見到有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d2dad54561320513318b7e2fb377bd960f2e39","tid":1677010,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:40:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a985d023e2b6120a7b7f5193572ba90fc937d40","tid":1677010,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:48:08.000Z","msg":"del 圖遮衣著再post"},{"pid":"394d5291104972ca765cccbc6cf6763000922a6f","tid":1677010,"uid":106870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:52:31.000Z","msg":"Push